Arrêt d'autobus 168 (Square-Victoria et McGill) et 12 (De l'Église).
-------
Message in English:
Lease transfer in Nuns' Island - Montreal;
Monthly rent: $ 1184;
1-bedroom apartment, 800 sqft, located at 201 Rue Corot, 15 minutes from downtown;
Panoramic view of downtown Montreal and Champlain Bridge;
Modern 15-storey building designed by famous architect Mies Van der Rohe;
The apartment is on the 7th floor, one bedroom, living room / dinning room, kitchen, bathroom, lots of storage;
Inclusions: Stove, fridge, dishwasher, heating, hot water;
Big laundry room in the basement with 12 washers and 10 dryers;
Gym, outdoor pool, sauna;
Big outdoor parking lot;
Indoor parking and lockers available;
Available from: July 1st, 2021;
Lease expiration: April 30th, 2022.
Possibility of renewal in November 2021;
Pet friendly;
Nearby: primary school, swimming pools, preschools, library, dog park, Couche Tard;
Bus stop 168 (Square-Victoria and McGill) and 12 (De l'Église)."]

