Magnificent apartment, in the Villeray district. The apartment is located on rue St-Denis near rue Villeray.
• Magnificent renovated, but whose original character has been preserved;
• Closed bedroom with large wardrobe;
• Appliances included (washer / dryer, refrigerator, oven and dishwasher)
• Unfurnished, with the possibility of purchasing certain items from the former tenant (bed, table and chairs);
• Non-smoker;
• Cat accepted;
